OL,3,CRefugees stage sit-in in bid for
OL,4,Canswers to homelessness
OL,6,FA number of refugees staged a sit in
OL,7,Fat a town hall asking for answers to
OL,8,Fwhere they should live after being
OL,9,Fmade homeless.
OL,11,FThe men and women have each fled their
OL,12,Fhomes, but are unable to find new ones
OL,13,Ffollowing the government's drive to
OL,14,Freduce the asylum seeker backlog.
OL,16,FMany have been evicted from their
OL,17,Fhomes after being granted the right to
OL,18,Flive in the UK - leaving them no
OL,19,Flonger eligible for asylum seeker
OL,20,Faccommodation.
