OL,3,CRefugees stage sit-in in bid for
OL,4,Canswers to homelessness
OL,6,FMilad is one of 15 who staged the sit
OL,7,Fin at Bury Town Hall. He is staying on
OL,8,Fthe floor of a nearby church, which is
OL,9,Flocked overnight.
OL,11,FHe told ITV Granada: "They open the
OL,12,Fdoors at 8pm every night, then at 10pm
OL,13,Flock them, then they re-open them at
OL,14,F8am the following morning. It is like
OL,15,Fa prison."
OL,17,FAnother refugees Zak goes to college
OL,18,Ffive times a week, but says without a
OL,19,Fhome he is finding it harder to do so.
