OL,6,F"I plan to leave my college because I
OL,7,Fam shy to sit next to someone without
OL,8,Fa shower," he said.
OL,10,FHe added: "Today we came to the town
OL,11,Fhall to ask for answers.
OL,13,F"We want to know how long we have to
OL,14,Fwait for accommodation.
OL,16,F"They say to us 'you have to sleep
OL,17,Foutside'. Some of us had a tent next
OL,18,Fto Tesco for a few months and no-one
OL,19,Fcares, and now we are fed up and we
OL,20,Fdon't know what we have to do."
