OL,6,FBury Council said: "We have every
OL,7,Fsympathy with people who have been
OL,8,Fthrown out of their homes due to the
OL,9,FHome Office policy of simply ending
OL,10,Faccommodation for people seeking
OL,11,Fasylum, whether their application was
OL,12,Faccepted or refused.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately our rough sleeper
OL,15,Faccommodation is now full and has a
OL,16,Fwaiting list due to the recent effects
OL,17,Fof migration on rough sleeping in the
OL,18,Fborough and any rough sleepers on the
OL,19,Fstreets is 80% due to migration issues
OL,20,Fand pressures."
