OL,4,Canswers to homelessness
OL,6,FSue McCann has been running English
OL,7,Fclasses for asylum seekers for three
OL,8,Fyears and said demand has flown
OL,9,Fthrough the roof.
OL,11,F"We used to average about eight
OL,12,Fpeople, but this year, in September,
OL,13,Fwe've got 37 on the register so I'm
OL,14,Fnow having to do two classes," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"I think it's a disgrace people are
OL,18,Fhaving to live in the way that they
OL,19,Fare with this uncertainty, poverty, no
OL,20,Fhouse, no real dream of establishing
OL,21,Fthemselves here."
