OL,6,FIn a statement the Home Office said:
OL,7,F"Once a newly recognised refugee is
OL,8,Fissued a biometric residence permit,
OL,9,Fthey get 28 days to move on from
OL,10,Fasylum accommodation.J"Support is also
OL,11,Favailable through Migrant Help and
OL,12,Ftheir partners, which includes advice
OL,13,Fon how to access Universal Credit, the
OL,14,Flabour market and where to get
OL,15,Fassistance with housing."
